{"tid":824170,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何志平涉貪】同時被捕卻未被起訴 前塞內加爾外長獲撤控或轉任污點證人","createTime":"2018-09-17T03:32:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T07:37:34.000Z","uid":17506,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e3dc36ffdd8603ecf5ff5d288cd98766304dfc59","tid":824170,"uid":17506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T03:32:50.000Z","msg":"前民政事務局局長何志平涉貪在美國被檢控，至今仍在還柙。同案另一被告、前塞內加爾外長加迪奧（Cheikh Gadio）日前卻獲司法部撤銷控罪。有美國律師認為加迪奧可能會轉做污點證人，將對何志平帶來很大影響。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指，何志平在2014年至2017年間，在加迪奧的協助下賄賂乍得總統，另外又涉嫌向烏干達的外長及總統提供利益，為其背後的能源企業換取生意上的好處。根據起訴書，何志平在2015年由香港、經紐約銀行匯款40萬美元到加迪奧的杜拜戶口。<br />\n<br />\n2人去年11月被捕，何志平12月即被正式起訴，不准保釋，但加迪奧獲准保釋在家軟禁，此後司法部一直未有正式起訴，根據法庭文件，雙方反而持續磋商，但外界不知商討內容。<br />\n<br />\n直至近日，司法部正式決定撤銷對加迪奧的所有控罪，但未有說明原因。美國律師陳宏基早前接受訪問時表示，加迪奧一直未被起訴，很有可能正與政府討論轉做污點證人，提供案件的細節以換取減刑；若真的發生，將對何志平案件帶來很大的影響。<br />\n<br />\n另一美國律師Jae Lee早前受訪時亦稱，可以推斷加迪奧正在考慮與政府合作，因為政府在本案的主要目標明顯是何志平。他相信，何的律師團隊應該一早已有計算加迪奧轉做污點證人的可能性，何有必要告訴律師，究竟加迪奧知道的案件細節有幾多，以思考屆時的應付策略。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180917/58690274\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180917%2F58690274&d=Sha41oWSewozM7Uf%2BQdNNQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=2bf71907\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180917%2F58690274&h=59f772d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180917/58690274</a>"},{"pid":"1f2c3170878d8501111d9f84eef8bafd4e20503e","tid":824170,"uid":134323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T03:34:17.000Z","msg":"肥仔平下半世有排坐"},{"pid":"637aaca8d6a4d29eb76f52636e2d547b5335563a","tid":824170,"uid":52881,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T03:39:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n來生唔好再做走狗啦肥平"},{"pid":"411662dc5de325577ffd8af374c8c9191c0408cf","tid":824170,"uid":47819,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T03:41:41.000Z","msg":"慢慢係美國坐過世呀肥平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8579be56c20c8fce9b6ae73f30ef78bee62119de","tid":824170,"uid":130105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T03:42:27.000Z","msg":"唔講唔記得，重坐緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"791319ec41ac71acd742f0db9a7f9aeffb29ba37","tid":824170,"uid":45830,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T03:45:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/17/114542_4e86000449eecd57b8a90741d59a94cf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2F114542_4e86000449eecd57b8a90741d59a94cf.jpg&h=962eaf60&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3251b052d0db18093aa62bdc43d44ff5004c8206","tid":824170,"uid":56999,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T03:46:35.000Z","msg":"為國捐軀"},{"pid":"568c1a6cd305d2edebafae7dc67325bbfaaedbaa","tid":824170,"uid":126305,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T04:10:02.000Z","msg":"下個幾時到董建華？"},{"pid":"c6593a3869dd379ca3f79b31d42e883fc3b7ac0a","tid":824170,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T05:55:06.000Z","msg":"你還有党<br />\n<br />\n整返個志平精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f822f3cdcfdea37c2c7b73e4f38c34243c56109d","tid":824170,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f2c3170878d8501111d9f84eef8bafd4e20503e","tid":824170,"uid":134323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T03:34:17.000Z","msg":"肥仔平下半世有排坐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-1